Package org.ontal.imgutil.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdjustedImage
    OImage implementation class oriented to process and transform image according to "adjust" processing strategy (ADJUST) provided in the Settings parameter during the constructor call.
    ExpandedImage
    OImage implementation class oriented to process and transform image according to "expand" processing strategy (EXPAND) provided in the Settings parameter during the constructor call.
    FitImage
    OImage implementation class oriented to process and transform image according to "fit" processing strategy (FIT) provided in the Settings parameter during the constructor call.
    LimitedImage
    OImage implementation class oriented to process and transform image according to "limit" processing strategy (LIMIT) provided in the Settings parameter during the constructor call.
    TiledImage
    OImage implementation class oriented to process and transform image according to "tile" processing strategy (TILE) provided in the Settings parameter during the constructor call.
